data.value: Circles are omnipresent in our lives. The moon, the sun, and the earth are circles. Even the blood that flows in our body is in constant circulation to maintain life, and the bubbles we exhale while diving also look like circles. In other words: Life itself is a circle. A circle stands for safety and security… and nothing is more important when you go diving!

data.value: Our diving center is located in the middle of Ras Umm el Sid area, also known as Hadaba, in El Ferouseya Street. We are surrounded by many 3* to 5* resorts and the shopping street, Il Mercato. Our house reef in Naama Bay is a 10 minute drive from the diving center. So come visit us, we are looking forward to welcoming you at our diving center very soon.
